action.description: Taken from Chief Clerk's desk.Placed on General File.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 774.)Dispensed with reprinting.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved, as amended. (Yeas: 27, Nays: 15.)To printer.From printer. To reengrossment. Reengrossed. Fourth reprint.To Senate.In Senate.
